  \
  \ allocate-xstack ( n -- a )
  \
  \ Create an `xstack` in the heap. _n_ is the size in
  \ cells.  Return its address _a_.
  \
  \ See also: `xfree`, `allocate-xstack`.
  \
  \ }doc

