  \ doc{
  \
  \ allot-xstack ( n -- a )
  \
  \ Create an `xstack` in data space. _n_ is the size in
  \ cells.  Return its address _a_.
  \
  \ See also: `allocate-xstack`.
  \
  \ }doc

